00:11:12.640 --> 00:11:14.040
Grandpa's amazing!

00:11:14.440 --> 00:11:16.440
If you can gather one thousand taels

00:11:17.040 --> 00:11:18.600
within a single day

00:11:18.600 --> 00:11:20.480
to support the army,

00:11:21.160 --> 00:11:22.080
I might

00:11:22.440 --> 00:11:25.000
consider reuniting your family.

00:11:25.000 --> 00:11:26.640
General, there's only nine hundred taels.

00:11:27.000 --> 00:11:28.280
I'll find the remaining hundred

00:11:28.400 --> 00:11:29.520
as soon as possible.

00:11:29.720 --> 00:11:32.040
There's no room for negotiation.

00:11:34.120 --> 00:11:36.400
You'd better stop dreaming.

